// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0003 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e817803c-7a44-5854-a5e0-4dc16abedf9e

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
